. To compile or run the server
  - First run the following commands to install the dependent packages.
    $ go mod init blockchaindb
    $ go mod tidy
    $ go mod vendor
  - Then run compile.sh
    $ ./compile.sh
  - To run the server with id n
    $ ./start.sh --id=n

. To run the test
  $ go run ./test/test_name.go
